text: right Saranskoe, Saranskoye (; , Лаукишкен; ) is a rural locality (selo) in Kaliningrad Oblast. In the Prussian era, this town belonged to Landkreis Labiau/Kreis Labiau (de), in the Province of East Prussia. ==People== * Rogalla von Bieberstein (de) * Gustav Glogau * Herbert W.
